      "acceptanceCriteria": "Not required at MRL 2 for this factor.",
      "rationale": "Model form uncertainty (turbulence model selection, hemolysis constitutive law) is not required to be formally assessed at MRL 2. The SST k-omega turbulence model and Giersiepen-Wurzinger power-law hemolysis model were selected based on published literature consensus for blood pump applications."
