      "rationale": "All model inputs are documented in the simulation input file archive. Pump geometry was digitized from manufacturer CAD files with dimensional tolerance ±0.05 mm. Boundary conditions derive from clinical measurement data (2025 dataset). Blood viscosity model parameters are sourced from peer-reviewed rheology studies. Input uncertainty propagation was performed for the three most sensitive parameters."
