    "outcome": "Accepted",
    "rationale": "All seven assessed credibility factors meet or exceed the required levels for MRL 2. The six not-assessed factors are consistent with the MRL 2 credibility plan for a Class II device. Validation evidence demonstrates RH < 1 at all five operating points with mean normalized error of 8.3%, within the pre-specified acceptance band. The model is accepted for use in identifying worst-case hemolysis operating conditions for CPB device regulatory submission.",
